Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 以世界为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 战斗 不停战斗的黑色勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于真正崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色勇者被守护世界的女神们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印在南端的遥远尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 那里还住着另一个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太过丑陋 无比孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独得快要死掉的寂寞恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能将你的身体给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃掉你的半边身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的第一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你 我的身体根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被称为「所有公式」的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便分成了「解开所有公式者」和「编造所有公式者」两部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而勇者立刻吃掉了「编造所有公式者」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者将世界不断破坏 破坏 破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到达了其中心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那里只有漆黑的绝望 痛楚 孤独 地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及黑暗 黑暗 黑暗 黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想破坏整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却要在这之前死去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来代替我承受这黑暗和痛楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用我剩下的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将黑暗放进这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的恶魔 并没感到有多后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为即使只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为朋友而活过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的恶魔 是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后 也是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩那家伙好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人叫来自己却不在是怎么回事 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉乌前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们被叫来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}远去时日的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看起来像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你接下来打算把我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道有一天会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:04:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始觉得事情会好转 可以一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就总是会突然变成这种局面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在你手下 或许也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能被你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊 就算我这种人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也有个傻瓜会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经答应她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能杀我的人已经定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲莉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打破约定的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是把你当成挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你还是要杀我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定决定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束一切吧 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还结束不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢 上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求…雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一切都是我下令研制的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这个国家干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 很普通的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只选择了一些必要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说因为必要就进行了人体实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底背负了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要一个人背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我帮不了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你还把我当外人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是挚友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊 席恩·阿斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不会放弃的 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你牛角尖钻得多深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何陷入黑暗 无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会放弃你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你杀害同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起走吧 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救出哭成这样的你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的决定果然是正确的 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救你 无论世界变成怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的挚爱 寂寞的恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 我才拔出了剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了吗 到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 在永远的地狱徘徊的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将你送去那里 送去 送去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 α吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是α吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将化为「真」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「编造所有公式者」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然会做到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有点轻视你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快制止他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是很想吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在还不到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键的他还是这种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样改变不了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救不了任何人 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括他 也包括你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还包括你最重视的那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你似乎还留有一点理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理智？你竟然会说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想看看你身上的理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 席恩不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他绝不会失去理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我选择了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他总是会选择正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩会背叛你 莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑陋的野兽 悲哀的恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前你就继续玩你的友情游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂他心中苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打着无聊的正义和爱的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一如既往地睡你的安稳觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩…

Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别睡啦 快起床 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡糊涂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 让我帮你干活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己却先阵亡了 这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡着了吗 睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四小时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那些都是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实 好像做了很…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的刚才我还记着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像是很令人不快的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还好我把你叫醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 帮大忙了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说了什么「被熟女的胸罩包围我真是太幸福了」之类的梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直犹豫着要不要叫醒你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了 我的爱好泄底了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃不…你这么爽快就承认了 真是一点都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经做完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你给我上床好好睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你一个人把那些全解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛不叫醒我而自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 因为我叫你也不醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 啰嗦啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别管了 快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 睡了四小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以和你继续工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀 杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在此杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳就连死都死不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会永远…在地狱里徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我要 把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从黑暗里救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赢了 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀不了这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有人赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我们好脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要将朋友当做祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打进地狱 再向前进？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可我是连杀莱纳…救莱纳都做不到的懦夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再苛责自己了 你的选择没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你不必再苦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 接下来我会解决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人 这里禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 结果那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没杀我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 看守大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问你点事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不在就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出一副那样的表情 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么？我还想问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说…你真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…找了好久 一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩说的话我也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在找 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过席恩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他变得好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑着说他杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得像要哭出来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你不可能杀莱纳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他 还是一直笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我不要再去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也别跟他扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他向奈尔法皇国出兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领用禁忌之术创造的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将奈尔法人民全部杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国人民都为他而狂热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他是英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要统治世界的英雄王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都疯了 大家都疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩 大家 整个国家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用再担心任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄王 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们逃了 追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了又怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寻找 阻止他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去揭开真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要平安逃掉啊 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着也跟死了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能留在人身边 也不能爱别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就放弃了一切生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被你拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从心底被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原·红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃色的头发？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想回报你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在虽然不知道你深陷什么困境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会去到你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此不知道需要多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但需要的我都会弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好觉悟等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你后悔那时没有杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一个人擅自陷入绝望 背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要哭泣的你 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认你有一个最棒的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也会前进的 席恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放弃你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯



